  "status": 401,
  "data": {
    "message": "Invalid signature"
  }
}
```

## POST /callback/agregator/digiflazz

Callback dari Digiflazz.

### Success

```json
{
  "status": 200,
  "data": {
    "message": "OK"
  }
}
```

